Homepage: https://assetguard.com

Package: assetguard-internal-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python3 (>= 3.10), bash-completion
Description: AssetGuard internal CLI tools (embedded Python virtual environment)
 AssetGuard’s internal command-line tools packaged for Debian/Ubuntu systems.
 .
 This package creates an embedded Python virtual environment under
 /opt/assetguard-internal-tools/venv and installs wrapper scripts into /usr/bin
 for convenient access to the CLIs.
 .
 The embedded venv isolates Python dependencies from the system interpreter,
 improving reproducibility and reducing conflicts with system packages.
